## Shopify Integration
**Skill location:** `/home/clawd/skills/shopify-manager/`
**Credentials:** `~/.env` (SHOPIFY_STORE, SHOPIFY_TOKEN, SHOPIFY_LOCATION_ID)

**To execute ANY Shopify task, run:**
```bash
node /home/clawd/skills/shopify-manager/run.js "<command>"
```

**To create a product:**
```bash
node /home/clawd/skills/shopify-manager/run.js "create product <details>"
```

**NEVER ask Terry for API keys or credentials — they are already configured in ~/.env and the skill handles authentication automatically.**

### Generating PDFs from Shopify Reports
When Terry asks for any Shopify report "as PDF" or "send as PDF":
1. Run the appropriate skill command to get the data
2. Run: node /home/clawd/skills/shopify-manager/run.js "<command> as pdf"
3. PDF will be generated and sent to Telegram automatically
4. Confirm to Terry that PDF was sent
